{"type":null,"faqId":11974,"title":"G620-L72  忘记屏幕解锁密码或图案，如何解决？","answer":"&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">您可以通过升级手机的方法解决。升级后，手机内部存储中的数据将被删除。</span> \n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">通过</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡升级：</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-3cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Book Antiqua','serif';\"><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>步骤 1<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入</span> <span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn</a> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，根据手机型号下载软件升级包。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-3cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Book Antiqua','serif';\"><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>步骤 2<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">将升级包中的</span><span> dload </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文件夹放入</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡根目录下。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-3cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Book Antiqua','serif';\"><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>步骤 3<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机在关机状态下，插入</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡，同时按住电源键和音量上下键直到出现安卓机器人图标，手机进入升级模式开始升级。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">升级完成后手机将会恢复出厂设置。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若无法升级，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":1,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2757","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398821806000,"seriesProductName":"G620-L72","visitedTimes":463,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"忘记屏幕解锁密码或图案","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}